-- Taiwan's Cathay Financial says open to buying more shares in RCBC
-- 
-- Wed Dec 17, 2014 02:21AM EST
-- None



MANILA, Dec 17 (Reuters) - Cathay Financial Holding Co Ltd <2882.TW> is open to buying more shares in Rizal Commercial Banking Corp (RCBC) <RCB.PS>, its president said on Wednesday.

Cathay Financial said on Tuesday its board had approved its insurance unit's 17.9 billion peso ($400 million) investment in RCBC, taking a 20 percent stake in the Philippines' ninth largest lender by assets. [ID:nL3N0TZ36N]